                <h2>Organizational Structure & Reorganizations</h2>
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> Booz Allen operates with a matrix organization, structuring around key **Markets (Defense, National Security, Civil)** and integrating specialized **Functional/Technology Capabilities (Cyber, AI, Engineering)** across those markets.</p>
                <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
