                <h3>Recent Reorganizations & Strategic Shifts</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Continuous Shift to Solutions/Technology Focus:</strong> Ongoing organizational alignment to emphasize **Artificial Intelligence, Cyber, and Digital Engineering** as core, high-growth offerings (part of the VoC strategy).</li>
                    <li><strong>Global Headquarters Relocation (2027 Projected):</strong> Strategic move of Global HQ from McLean to **Reston, Virginia**, designed to optimize facilities and foster next-generation technology work environments.</li>
                    <li><strong>Acquisitions-Driven Integration:</strong> Integration of key acquisitions (e.g., EverWatch) to strategically consolidate and expand high-value **National Security** and cyber capabilities.</li>
                </ul>
