                        <tr>
                            <td class="strength">STRENGTHS</td>
                            <td>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong class="strength">Deep Government Penetration:</strong> Decades-long, trusted relationships across **all US Intelligence and Defense agencies**.</li>
                                    <li><strong class="strength">Technology Leadership:</strong> Recognized lead in mission-critical **Cybersecurity and AI/Data Science** solutions.</li>
                                    <li><strong class="strength">Talent Base:</strong> Superior reputation for cleared personnel (high volume of **TS/SCI** clearances).</li>
                                </ul>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Leidos:</strong> Greater scale in large IT infrastructure, hardware integration, and broader contract value.</li>
                                    <li><strong>CACI:</strong> Highly focused and successful in providing proprietary, high-margin technology/products.</li>
                                    <li><strong>SAIC:</strong> Strong presence in logistics and platform integration, offering different diversification risk.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="weakness">WEAKNESSES</td>
                            <td>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong class="weakness">Revenue Concentration:</strong> Extremely reliant on the **U.S. Federal Government** (~97% of revenue), making it highly sensitive to budget cycles and political shifts.</li>
                                    <li><strong class="weakness">Legacy Perception:</strong> Still contends with the perception of a "consulting" firm despite the pivot to technology, creating competitive friction with pure-play integrators.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Leidos/SAIC:</strong> More diversified revenue streams outside of core Defense/Intelligence (e.g., Civil, Health IT).</li>
